---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Maple Tyne Technologies" description="At Maple-Tyne Technologies Inc., we believe in sovereign data privacy.">
	<main class="page-container">
    <section class="page-header">
      <h1 class="gradient-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
    </section>

		<div class="content-section">
      <p>At Maple-Tyne Technologies Inc., we believe in sovereign data privacy.</p>

      <p>Our flagship intelligent energy systems are built with a local-first architecture, ensuring that your household operational patterns stay entirely private on local hardware.</p>

      <p>We guarantee zero operational dependency on external cloud servers, which fully immunizes your home against server-side data breaches and unexpected internet outages.</p>

      <p>For our broader web platforms and digital utilities, we employ lightweight, secure deployment strategies that prioritize client-side execution to minimize data collection and rigorously protect user privacy.</p>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-container {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .content-section p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>
